        <h2 id="technology">Technology</h2>
        <p>I learned Computer Science pretty late, half way through college. I have now a lot of experience in front-end development. I enjoy designing, implementing, and observe people using interfaces I have created! I have come a long way, starting with Sencha Touch and then AngularJS. But I felt in love with EmberJS. Built by the same folks who crafted Ruby on Rails, based entirely on strong conventions and separation of concerns. Lovely!</p>

